						<p><hi rend="bold">King: ⎯⎯ Year: ⎯⎯</hi></p>						

						<p>This record may be assigned to the 10 century A.D. on grounds of palaeography.</p>						

						<p>This is a highly damaged record and seems to register a grant of land, free of all taxes. The name of the ruling king is unfortunately, lost. Also contains imprecatory portion.</p>						

